{"id": "cos052", "name": "Audio_Home_683_07_09", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">BASTARD! This guy too, that guy too... none of these bastards believe me!</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "Things breaking"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "For the past few decades, all the things I have done for you people, all the items I had excavated... and this is how you repay me!? A suspension!? \"Honorable employee\"... What the goddamn f*** is this garbage bulls***!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">You sons of b******! If you don't believe me, then open my brain! Dissect it all you want! You'll get to see the sight of those damn Architects attacking us...</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Sighs...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... Father?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin, it's me.</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "What's the matter, mothe... Yikes! Your face...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "It's okay... I'm fine.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "The first-aid kit is downstairs. I'll go get it...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "No, he has fallen asleep. Don't disturb him... I have something to tell you.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Tell me...?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin... let's leave this home.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "Things crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "L, leave?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "I know you are very surprised. But we've been working so hard, yet he just couldn't come out of it. He just kept thinking that A.R.C. doesn't believe him... then venting all his anger on us...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "You should understand, right? The dignified and prideful Colin has already disappeared in the forbidden areas. He will never come back again. Right now, he is nothing more than a violent drunkard...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mother... I...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "I know... I also hope he can recover and return to his previous self again. In my mind, he is still my husband... but for the past year, I feel like... I just can't take it anymore... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "I've already contacted my household. We'll be leaving soon... Colin, come with me. If you keep staying here, your life will be ruined by him as well. You're just sixteen. You can't...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... Sorry, mother. I... I can't go with you.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "W, why?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mother... I know how tough things have been for you this past year. That's why I understand your decision to leave... but if I leave him as well, father will truly lose everything. He'll never, ever return to normal again... It's like I abandoned my own father and left him to die all alone.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "As his son... I just can't let that happen. I can't do that.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I'm sorry, mother... I will figure out a way to keep father here. If the situation calls for it, I'll ask Grace to help too. You should leave for a safe place as soon as possible.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Then what about you?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I'll continue to work hard... No, work even harder than I did before. I'll let father know, that I achieved his expectations for me. Then, he'll wake up from his nightmare too. We can finally get together as a family again.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<i><font size=\"1.6\">... *Sobs*...</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mother?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "... In mother's mind, you're always that little boy who fell off a horse and sat there with a beaming smile... But when I didn't notice, you've grown up already. You're now a man capable of making this kind of decision yourself.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "Things breaking"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Huh! He's awake... Mother, go! Now!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Okay... Colin, no matter what, mother will always be proud of you. I'm really sorry, but I'll leave your father to you, okay?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yes. I'll take care of father. Here, leave from the side gate.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "I love you, my son...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I love you too... mom.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Booze? Where is my Booze?\nGimme the Booze...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia! Grace! Get the f*** over here!</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Father's... hope...\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">くそ！どいつもこいつも……私を信じようとしない！</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "物が割れる音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "この数10年私がお前らのためにどれほどのことをしてきたと思っている？\nどれほどのものを発見したと思っている？\nそれを解雇だと！？\nそれがお前たちの私に対する仕打ちなのか！？\n「栄誉職員」……くそ！それがなんだ！！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "ドアを閉める"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">くそが！バカが！能無しが！\n私の脳みそを解剖してみてみろ！\nアーキテクトたちが我々を攻撃してくる様子を……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ハァ……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "ノック"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……父さん？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin、私よ。</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "どうし……うわ！顔が……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "大丈夫よ……母さんは大丈夫。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "薬箱が下にあります。\n今すぐ取りに……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "いえ、いいの。\nあの人は眠ったわ。\nあまり騒音は立てないであげて……\nあなたにね、話があるの。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "話……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……この家を出ましょう。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "で、出る……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "驚かせてしまったわよね。\nでも、私たちはこんなに努力しているのに、あの人は一向に出てこようとしない。\nただただA.R.C.はあの人を信じてくれないと……\nそして、怒りの矛先を私たちに向けてくる……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "分かるでしょう？\nあの威厳のある誇り高きColinはもう存在しないの。\nあの人は封鎖エリアでいなくなってしまったの。\nもう二度と返ってくることはない。\n今のあの人は……ただの凶暴な酔っ払いよ……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母さん……僕は……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "そうよね……\n母さんもあの人が元に戻ってくれればいいと願っているわ。\n心の中では、あの人はまだ私の夫だもの……\nでも、あれから1年……もう限界なのよ……っ……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "もうね、実家には話してあるの。\n今日の内にこの家から出ていくわ……\nColin、あなたも一緒に行きましょう。\nここにとどまり続ければ、あなたの人生もあの人によって滅茶苦茶にされてしまうわ。\nあなたはまだ16歳なのよ。\nそんなのいけないわ……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……ごめんなさい。母さん、僕は……僕は行けません。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "ど、どうして？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母さん……この1年あなたはとても苦しんだ。\n……だからこそ、ここを出ていく決断をしたのだと分かっています……\nでも、僕まで出て行ってしまえば、父さんには何もなくなってしまう。\n元に戻る希望がなくなってしまう……\nそれは、僕が実の父親のことを捨てるのと同じだ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "人の子として……そんなことはできません。\n僕には、できないんです。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ごめんなさい、母さん……\n父さんのことは僕に任せてください。\n必要であれば、Graceにも手伝ってもらいます。\n母さんは早くここを出て、安全な場所へ行ってください。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "あなたは、どうするの？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "僕は今まで通り……いや、これまで以上に努力します。\n父さんに、僕は父さんの期待に応えたと知ってもらうんです。\nそうすれば、父さんの目も覚めるかもしれない。\nまた、家族で一緒に暮らせるかもしれない。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……うぅ……っ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母さん？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "……いつまでも子供だと……あの馬から落ちてもニコニコ笑っているような子供だと思っていたけれど……いつのまにか、こんなに大きく成長していたのね……\n自分でこんな決断を下せるほどに。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "物が割れる音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "！目を覚ましたのか……？\n母さん！急いで！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "分かったわ……Colin、どんな時でもあなたは母さんの自慢の子供よ。\nごめんなさい。\n父さんのことをよろしくね。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "はい、父さんのことは僕に任せてください。\nほら、ここから出て……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "愛しているわ。私の可愛い息子……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "僕も、母さんを愛しています……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "酒はどこだ……私の酒はどこだ……\n持ってこい……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia！Grace！早く来い！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "父さんの……希望……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">渾蛋！不管哪個傢伙……都不信我！</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "這幾十年，老子幫你們做了多少事、挖掘了多少東西，現在竟然用解雇來報答我！？「榮耀職員」……他○的算什麼東西！！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">你們這群狗娘養的廢物！來剖開我的腦袋看看啊，那些建造者攻擊我們的樣子……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……爸？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin，是我。</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "怎麼了，媽……哇！妳的臉……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "沒事……我沒事的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "藥箱在樓下，我去拿……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "不，他睡著了，別驚動他……我有話和你說。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "有話……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……我們離開這個家吧。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "離、離開？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我知道你很驚訝，但我們都這麼努力了，他卻始終走不出來，只覺得 A.R.C. 都不相信他……然後把氣出在我們身上……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "你應該明白吧？那個威嚴與驕傲的 Colin 已經消失在封鎖區，不會再回來了，現在的他，只是個凶暴的酒鬼……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽……我……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我懂……我也希望他能恢復過來，在心裡，他仍然是我的丈夫……但這一年來，我覺得我已經到了極限……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我已經和老家說過了，等等就走……Colin，你也一起來吧，再繼續待在這裡，你的人生也會被他給毀掉的。你才十六歲，不能這樣……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……抱歉，媽，我……我不能去。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "為、為什麼？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽……我明白這一年下來妳有多辛苦，所以才會選擇離開……但要是連我也走了，那爸就真的一無所有，再也沒辦法恢復正常了……那等於我拋棄了自己的親生父親。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "身為人子……不能讓那樣的事發生。我做不到。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "對不起，媽……我會想辦法拖住爸的，必要的話，也會請 Grace 幫忙。妳趕快離開，到安全的地方去吧。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "那你怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我會繼續努力……不，比以前更加努力，讓爸知道，我達成了他對我的期望。這樣一來，他也會清醒的，我們一家就能夠團聚了。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "……在媽媽心中，你一直都和當年一樣，是個會從馬背上跌下來、滿臉傻笑的小男孩……沒想到，你已經長大了，能做出這樣的決定了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唔，醒了嗎……媽，快走吧！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好……Colin，無論如何，你都是媽媽值得驕傲的兒子。對不起，爸爸就交給你了，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯，爸就交給我。來，從側門離開吧。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我愛你，兒子……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我也愛妳……媽。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "酒呢？我的酒呢？\n拿酒過來……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia！Grace！快給我滾過來！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "爸爸的……希望……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">개자식들! 누구도......날 믿어 주지 않아!</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "깨지는 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "수십 년 동안 이 몸이 너희를 위해 공헌한 일이 얼마나 되는지는 알고 있기나 해!? 내가 발굴해낸 것들이 얼마나 되는지 알면서 그러는 거냐고! 그래서... 그거 대한 보답이... 해고!?.... 「명예 멤버」......!? 개 같은 소리 하지 말라 그래!!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "문이 닫힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">쓰레기 같은 개자식들! 내 뇌를 해부해서라도 그 장면을 봤어야 한다고! 아키텍트들이... 우리를 공격했던 모습을...</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "하아......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......아버지?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin, 나란다.</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "무슨 일이세요, 어머니.... 으앗! 얼굴이...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "괜찮아......엄마는 괜찮아.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "구급 상자가 아래층에 있어요. 제가 가서...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "아니야.\n그 사람이 자고 있을 땐, 괜히 시끄럽게 굴 필요는 없을 것 같구나... 엄마가... 할 말이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "할... 말이요?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin......우리는 이 집을 떠나기로 했단다.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "떠, 떠나다니요...?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "놀라게 해서 미안하구나. 하지만 우린 충분히 노력했어. 네 아버지는 방에서 나오질 않고 A.R.C.가 자신을 믿어주지 않는다고만 생각하고 있으니... 결국 그 분노가 우리에게까지...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "넌 이미 알고 있지? 그 엄숙하고 자부심이 넘쳤던 Colin은 봉쇄구역에서 이미 죽어버린 거나 다름없게 됐어. 다시는 돌아오지 못해. 지금의 네 아버지는 그저... 흉폭한 주정뱅이일 뿐이야...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어머니...... 저는......\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "이해한다......나도 저 이가 하루빨리 정상으로 돌아오길 바라고 있어. 그래도  내 남편이니까... 하지만 이 1년 동안은... 나도 이제 한계인 것 같구나.... 흑...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "친가 쪽에는 이미 이야기해두었단다..... Colin, 너도 함께 가자꾸나. 이곳에 계속 머물다가는 네 인생도 망가질 수 있어. 넌 아직 16살밖에 안 됐잖니. 여기에 있는 것보다는...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......죄송해요, 어머니... 전... 갈 수 없어요.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "어, 어째서?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어머니...... 이 1년 동안 어머니께서 얼마나 고생하셨는지 잘 알고 있어요. 그리고 이런 결정을 내리신 마음까지도... 하지만 저까지 떠나버리면, 아버지는 정말로 아무것도 아닌 사람이 돼버릴 거예요. 그리고 정상으로 회복할 수 있는 작은 가능성조차 사라져버릴 거예요... 그건... 제 스스로 가족을 버리는 거나 마찬가지잖아요.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "아들의 도리로써...... \n그렇게는 할 수 없을 것 같아요.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "죄송해요, 어머니... 제가 아버지를 구할 방법을 생각해낼 거예요. 도움이 필요하면, Grace에게도 부탁을 할 거고요. 어머니는 이곳을 떠나 안전한 곳에 가 계세요.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "그럼 너는? 너는 어떡하려고 그러니?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "저는 계속 노력... 아니, 전보다 훨씬 더 노력해서 아버지께서 제게 거신 기대에 부응하는 모습을 보여줄 생각이에요. 그러면 아버지의 상태도 더 나아지고  우리 가족이 다시 한자리에 모일 수도 있게 될 거예요.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......흑......</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어머니?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "......엄마 마음속에서 너는... 예전 말을 타다가 떨어지고도 싱글벙글 웃는 어린아이의 모습으로 남아있단다... 어느새 이런 결정을 스스로 내릴 만큼 성장했구나.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "깨지는 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "! 깨어났나 봐요... 어머니, 어서 가세요!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "그래......Colin, 어떤 일이 생겨도 넌 엄마가 가장 자랑스러워하는 아들이란다. 미안하구나. 아버지는 네게 맡길게. 그래도 괜찮겠니?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "네. 아버지는 제게 맡기세요. 자, 이쪽 문으로 나가세요.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "사랑한다, 아들아...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "저도 사랑해요......어머니.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "술 어딨어... 내 술 어딨어!?\n술 어딨냐고......!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia! Grace! 당장 튀어오지 못해!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "아버지의...... 희망......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">渾蛋！不管哪個傢伙……都不信我！</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "這幾十年，老子幫你們做了多少事、挖掘了多少東西，現在竟然用解雇來報答我！？「榮耀職員」……他○的算什麼東西！！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">你們這群狗娘養的廢物！來剖開我的腦袋看看啊，那些建造者攻擊我們的樣子……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……爸？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin，是我。</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "怎麼了，媽……哇！妳的臉……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "沒事……我沒事的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "藥箱在樓下，我去拿……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "不，他睡著了，別驚動他……我有話和你說。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "有話……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……我們離開這個家吧。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "離、離開？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我知道你很驚訝，但我們都這麼努力了，他卻始終走不出來，只覺得 A.R.C. 都不相信他……然後把氣出在我們身上……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "你應該明白吧？那個威嚴與驕傲的 Colin 已經消失在封鎖區，不會再回來了，現在的他，只是個凶暴的酒鬼……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽……我……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我懂……我也希望他能恢復過來，在心裡，他仍然是我的丈夫……但這一年來，我覺得我已經到了極限……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我已經和老家說過了，等等就走……Colin，你也一起來吧，再繼續待在這裡，你的人生也會被他給毀掉的。你才十六歲，不能這樣……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……抱歉，媽，我……我不能去。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "為、為什麼？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽……我明白這一年下來妳有多辛苦，所以才會選擇離開……但要是連我也走了，那爸就真的一無所有，再也沒辦法恢復正常了……那等於我拋棄了自己的親生父親。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "身為人子……不能讓那樣的事發生。我做不到。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "對不起，媽……我會想辦法拖住爸的，必要的話，也會請 Grace 幫忙。妳趕快離開，到安全的地方去吧。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "那你怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我會繼續努力……不，比以前更加努力，讓爸知道，我達成了他對我的期望。這樣一來，他也會清醒的，我們一家就能夠團聚了。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "媽？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "……在媽媽心中，你一直都和當年一樣，是個會從馬背上跌下來、滿臉傻笑的小男孩……沒想到，你已經長大了，能做出這樣的決定了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唔，醒了嗎……媽，快走吧！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好……Colin，無論如何，你都是媽媽值得驕傲的兒子。對不起，爸爸就交給你了，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯，爸就交給我。來，從側門離開吧。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我愛你，兒子……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我也愛妳……媽。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "酒呢？我的酒呢？\n拿酒過來……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia！Grace！快給我滾過來！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "爸爸的……希望……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">浑蛋！不管哪个家伙……都不信我！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "这几十年，老子帮你们做了多少事、挖掘了多少东西，现在竟然用解雇来报答我！ ？ 「荣耀职员」……他○的算什么东西！ ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Slame", "关门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">你们这群狗娘养的废物！来剖开我的脑袋看看啊，那些建造者攻击我们的样子……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……爸？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Colin，是我。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "怎么了，妈……哇！妳的脸……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "没事……我没事的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "药箱在楼下，我去拿……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "不，他睡着了，别惊动他……我有话和你说。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "有话……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……我们离开这个家吧。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "离、离开？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我知道你很惊讶，但我们都这么努力了，他却始终走不出来，只觉得 A.R.C. 都不相信他……然后把气出在我们身上……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "你应该明白吧？那个威严与骄傲的 Colin 已经消失在封锁区，不会再回来了，现在的他，只是个凶暴的酒鬼……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "妈……我……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我懂……我也希望他能恢复过来，在心里，他仍然是我的丈夫……但这一年来，我觉得我已经到了极限……呜……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我已经和老家说过了，等等就走……Colin，你也一起来吧，再继续待在这里，你的人生也会被他给毁掉的。你才十六岁，不能这样……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……抱歉，妈，我……我不能去。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "为、为什么？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "妈……我明白这一年下来妳有多辛苦，所以才会选择离开……但要是连我也走了，那爸就真的一无所有，再也没办法恢复正常了……那等于我抛弃了自己的亲生父亲。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "身为人子……不能让那样的事发生。我做不到。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Colin……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "对不起，妈……我会想办法拖住爸的，必要的话，也会请 Grace 帮忙。妳赶快离开，到安全的地方去吧。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "那你怎么办？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我会继续努力……不，比以前更加努力，让爸知道，我达成了他对我的期望。这样一来，他也会清醒的，我们一家就能够团聚了。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……呜……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "妈？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "……在妈妈心中，你一直都和当年一样，是个会从马背上跌下来、满脸傻笑的小男孩……没想到，你已经长大了，能做出这样的决定了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_glass_02", "碎裂声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "唔，醒了吗……妈，快走吧！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好……Colin，无论如何，你都是妈妈值得骄傲的儿子。对不起，爸爸就交给你了，好吗？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯，爸就交给我。来，从侧门离开吧。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "我爱你，儿子……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我也爱妳……妈。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "酒呢？我的酒呢？\n拿酒过来……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Alyxia！ Grace！快给我滚过来！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "爸爸的……希望……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}